\[ 	ext{Angle } BAC = \frac{900}{7} - 45 = \frac{900}{7} - \frac{315}{7} = \frac{585}{7}. \] 
Thus, angle $BAC$ measures \boxed{\frac{585}{7}\text{ degrees}}.

What is the number of square centimeters in the area of this trapezoid?

[asy]
