What is the simplified value of $\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\div\frac{\sqrt{20}}{3\sqrt{25}}$? ||| \begin{align*}
\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\div\frac{\sqrt{20}}{3\sqrt{25}}&=\frac{\sqrt{24}}{\sqrt{30}}\times\frac{\sqrt{20}}{3\sqrt{25}} \\
&=\frac{4\sqrt{6}}{\sqrt{5}\times\sqrt{6}}\times\frac{\sqrt{20}}{15} \\
&=\frac{20}{15} = \frac{4}{3} \\ 
&= \boxed{\frac{4}{3}} 
\end{align*}

